  "where_it_fits": "Located under Institution > Clients in the top navigation and reachable via the Clients icon in the left sidebar, this module is the primary client administration area within the application where users view client listings, import/create clients, and manage client status and related accounts as part of routine operations.",
  "assumed_state_on_entry": "Authenticated user with permission to access the Institution > Clients section (or Clients sidebar shortcut)."
